HEADWORD: Centurist
<hw>Cen"tu*rist</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>centuriateur</ets>.]</ety> <def>An historian who distinguishes time
by centuries, esp. one of those who wrote the ⟦ldquo⟧Magdeburg
Centuries.⟦rdquo⟧ See under <er>Century</er>.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
